Five Teams From The Moi Educational Centre In Nairobi Will Honor The Invitation To Make Their Inaugural Appearance In The Norway Cup Set To Run From 27th July. The Teams In Different Age Categories Will Feature Alongside Local?Based Mathare Youth Sports Association. With Training Already In Progress, Concerned Parties Speaking During The School's Annual Football Gala Are Anticipating The 3?Day Tournament, With High Expectations Of A Good Show. The Teams Will Leave The Country On 22nd July.